os:20;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlCRzVMRkdTP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAay2ywjA5koc09rndv6OukNGpLfe-Ya2qvzYPB9hRbL-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09BG5LFGS" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fire HD 8 Kids</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlCRzZEU0JZP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAZAzeuQPqAqUDaxkW1-mu4nKLL94vWlGNkL8sJuRddD8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09BG6DSBY" class="rapid-with-clickid">Kids Pro 的</a>售价均为 75 美元。这标志着新低，比平均价格低 55 美元。这两款产品具有与上述 Fire HD 10 Kids 型号相同的额外功能，但它们使用 Fire HD 8 作为基础，因此速度或空间不那么大。不过，如果您想为您的孩子在流媒体和阅读机上省点钱，那么以这个价格来说，它们是物有所值的。</p><h2>三星 Galaxy Tab S8 </h2><p><core-commerce id="80846a887b814a6697f3726e89c7cb0f" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTR