4e83780</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 10:22:22 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689162965</ingested><modified> 2023-07-12T11:56:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="939" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/1fcc2290-2092-11ee-af3d-684a136432c9" width="1500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="939" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/1fcc2290-2092-11ee-af3d-684a136432c9" width="1500"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[8bitdo]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Hands holding a controller with an Xbox on top of a wooden table.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[8bitdo]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Discord bans teen dating servers and the sharing of AI-generated CSAM]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在有<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/social-media/discord-child-safety-social-platform-challenges-rcna89769">报道</a>称掠夺者一直在<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/discord-still-has-a-child-safety-issue-085304790.html">使用该应用程序</a>创建和传播儿童性虐待材料 (CSAM) 以及诱骗青少年后，Discord<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://discord.com/safety/commitment-to-teen-child-safety">更新了</a>旨在保护其平台上的儿童和青少年的政策。该平台现在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/discord-bans-teen-dating-servers-child-ai-sexualization-rcna93690">明确禁止</a>人工智能生成的真实感 CSAM。正如<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2023/06/19/artificial-intelligence-child-sex-abuse-images/"><em>《华盛顿邮报》</em></a>最近报道的那样，生成式人工智能的兴起也导致了带有儿童性描写的逼真图像的激增。该出版物<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/interactive/2022/artificial-intelligence-images-dall-e/?itid=lk_inline_manual_25">看到了</a>有关使用 Midjourney（Discord 上的文本到图像生成人工智能）来创建不恰当的儿童图像的讨论。</p><p>除了禁止人工智能生成的 CSAM 之外，Discord 现在还明确禁止任何其他类型的使儿童性化的文本或媒体内容。该平台还禁止青少年约会服务器，并誓言将对参与这种行为的用户采取行动。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/social-media/discord-child-safety-social-platform-challenges-rcna89769"><em>NBC 新闻</em></a>之前的一项调查发现，Discord 服务器被宣传为青少年约会服务器，参与者向未成年人索取裸照。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>此前，成人用户曾因在 Discord 上诱骗儿童而被起诉，甚至还有犯罪团伙勒索未成年用户发送自己的色情图片。完全禁止青少年约会服务器可能有助于缓解这个问题。 Discord 还在其政策中加入了一条内容，其中规定，如果发现年龄较大的青少年诱骗年龄较小的青少年，将“根据其与儿童的不当性行为和诱骗政策进行审查并采取行动”。</p><p>除了更新规则之外，Discord 最近还推出了一款<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/new-family-center-tool-gives-parents-better-insight-into-their-teens-discord-usage-150014579.html">家庭中心工具</a>，家长可以用它来关注孩子在聊天服务上的活动。虽然父母无法看到孩子消息的实际内容，但选择加入工具可以让他们看到孩子与谁是朋友以及他们在平台上与谁交谈。 Discord 希望这些新措施和工具能够与旧措施（包括使用 PhotoDNA 主动扫描上传到其平台的图像）一起帮助确保未成年用户的安全。 </p><div id="c42fe389823d4986968864e12ed93eaa"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Discord 的家庭中心是一个新的选择加入工具，使青少年可以轻松地让父母和监护人了解他们的 Discord 活动，同时尊重他们自己的自主权。 <a href="https://t.co/UFY0ybo0LR">pic.twitter.com/UFY0ybo0LR</a></p> — Discord (@discord) <a href="https://twitter.com/discord/status/1678783622969692165?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 11 日</a></blockquote></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/discord-bans-teen-dating-servers-and-the-sharing-of-ai- generated-csam-071626058.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/discord-bans-teen-dating-servers-and-the-sharing-of-ai-generated-csam-071626058.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b8e5c6ca-e236-4725-b39d-d60a3218a117</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 07:16:26 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689146183</ingested><modified> 2023-07-12T07:16:28+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Lifestyle]]></category><category><![CDATA[Family & Relationships]]></category><category><![CDATA[Cultural Groups]]></category><category><![CDATA[Society & Culture]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="2663" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/f93839c0-2078-11ee-bf77-4f136ab51c55" width="3994"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2663" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/f93839c0-2078-11ee-bf77-4f136ab51c55" width="3994"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A laptop keyboard and Discord logo displayed on a phone screen are seen in th